01:32:53,734 --> 01:32:54,708
TRAVIS: Allons prendre à boire.

1243
01:32:54,709 --> 01:32:55,799
MARISHA: Vous allez faire un bras de fer?

1244
01:32:55,800 --> 01:32:56,512
TRAVIS: Non.

1245
01:32:56,513 --> 01:33:03,320
MARISHA: Ok. Et un pierre, papier, ciseaux? Attends,
